id: pm-6zqq
title: Hybrid semantic reindex should emit bounded progress and deterministic JSON completion
description: Improve long semantic/hybrid reindex observability so agents get deterministic JSON completion details plus batch-level progress for local embedding runs.
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 0
tags[1]: pm-cli
created_at: "2026-05-10T22:12:09.922Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-13T05:13:09.426Z"
author: opencode-agent
acceptance_criteria: "Hybrid semantic reindex reports deterministic progress/noninteractive heartbeat, exits with JSON success or structured failure, and documents expected local-embedding runtime/resume behavior."
parent: pm-rnpb
resolution: Implemented deterministic semantic reindex progress and JSON completion summary.
expected_result: Agents can monitor long semantic/hybrid reindex runs and gate completion from JSON without parsing stderr.
actual_result: pm reindex --mode hybrid --progress --json reports semantic counts and batch progress; current tracker completed with 701 unchanged vectors skipped.
