  "2026-05-13T05:07:39.326Z",codex-audit,"Implementation evidence: reindex JSON now includes semantic.enabled/stale_items/unchanged_items/embedded_items/vector_upserted/batches_completed; --progress emits embedding_batch_start/complete with batch counts; real hybrid reindex on current tracker returned ok with 701 unchanged semantic vectors skipped and deterministic JSON completion. Verification passed: focused reindex/embedding/runtime tests, linked pm test, full coverage 91 files/1290 tests at 100 percent, static quality, docs-skills, tracked secret scan. Known non-code blockers remain pre-existing history drift and unresolved historical Sentry groups."
